{"type": "article", "id": 10868, "title": "你够有钱的话，就像这样在悬崖边盖个六面采光房吧", "description": "足够美。", "date": "2015-06-16T12:49:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 11586, "name": "阳光房"}, {"id": 11587, "name": "向日葵房"}, {"id": 11588, "name": "地中海"}, {"id": 272, "name": "建筑设计"}], "category": 17, "author": 37534, "comment_count": 14, "praise_count": 346, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702120539muXMV78d3ShNeHA0.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t没错，图中的这幢小房子坐落在悬崖边，它面朝地中海，主人给它起名叫“地中海之家”。房间呈立方体状，被粉刷成了白色，还涂有黑色的窗框。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120534DOtzJc47WEq29nBd.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"426\" title=\"由于海边常吹强风，窗户玻璃均被特别加厚了。\" alt=\"由于海边常吹强风，窗户玻璃均被特别加厚了。\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>由于海风强劲，窗户玻璃均被特别加厚了。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120534kd73fbEFPzLMZsTK.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"492\" title=\"地中海附近光照充足，房子使用的是太阳能集热器。\" alt=\"地中海附近光照充足，房子使用的是太阳能集热器。\" data-ratio=\"0.76875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>地中海附近光照充足，房子使用的是太阳能集热器。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120535ZIKXJnPw8UDmrz0d.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"440\" title=\"它是由巴塞罗那建筑事务所cadaval &amp; sola-morales设计的。\" alt=\"它是由巴塞罗那建筑事务所cadaval &amp; sola-morales设计的。\" data-ratio=\"0.6875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>它是由巴塞罗那建筑事务所 <a href=\"http://www.ca-so.com\" target=\"_blank\">cadaval &amp; sola-morales</a> 设计的。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120535QikdAm3SPJFUbpDw.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"426\" title=\"房子的设计充分考虑到了视野，还兼顾到了和周围环境的和谐。\" alt=\"房子的设计充分考虑到了视野，还兼顾到了和周围环境的和谐。\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>房子的设计充分考虑到了视野，还兼顾到了和周围环境的和谐。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120536eF7krfKEVJNxltU6.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"426\" title=\"其实房间一共分为上下两层，内部有一个楼梯将两层上下相连。\" alt=\"其实房间一共分为上下两层，内部有一个楼梯将两层上下相连。\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>其实房间一共有两层，内部的楼梯将上下两层相连。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120536Jl0mwir3WhejxtnX.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"481\" title=\"每一个小单元都有不同的面向和视野\" alt=\"每一个小单元都有不同的面向和视野\" data-ratio=\"0.7515625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>每一个小单元都有不同的面向和视野</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120537dfZgLBRMF97cja2p.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"445\" title=\"旁边还有一个小泳池\" alt=\"旁边还有一个小泳池\" data-ratio=\"0.6953125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>旁边还有一个小泳池</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120537rKLxPROcFT5v9msh.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"641\" title=\"这年头，度假房拼的都是颜值啊。\" alt=\"这年头，度假房拼的都是颜值啊。\" data-ratio=\"1.0015625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>这年头，度假房拼的都是颜值啊。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t这个叫作<a href=\"http://www.ca-so.com/project.php?project_id=14&amp;cat=1\" target=\"_blank\"> </a><span><a href=\"http://www.ca-so.com/project.php?project_id=14&amp;cat=1\" target=\"_blank\">cadaval &amp; sola-morales </a>的</span>工作室做了不少住房项目，他们好像特别偏爱“造型感强的房子<span>+</span>一个小泳池”的组合。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120538mwgFG6DYdIXt5srn.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"393\" title=\"X House，Cabrils，Barcelona.\" alt=\"X House，Cabrils，Barcelona.\" data-ratio=\"0.6140625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>X House，Cabrils，Barcelona.</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120538pIgO2sC50i9ZA71J.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"427\" title=\"House at the Pyrenees，Aran Valley. Spain.\" alt=\"House at the Pyrenees，Aran Valley. Spain.\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>House at the Pyrenees，Aran Valley. Spain.</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120539kuWTqsyYbMxhtDK5.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"401\" title=\"Tepoztlan, Morelos, Mexico\" alt=\"Tepoztlan, Morelos, Mexico\" data-ratio=\"0.6265625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>Tepoztlan，Morelos，Mexico</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<em>题图来源：</em><a href=\"http://www.designboom.com/architecture/sunflower-house-cadaval-and-sola-morales-costa-brava-06-13-2015/\" target=\"_blank\"><em>designboom</em></a> \r\n</p>\n\n"}